{"word":"H3868 - לוּז - lûwz - looz - Depart","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לוּז</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>lûwz"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>looz"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Depart"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரியாதிரு, அலட்சியம்பண்ணு, மாறுபாடாயிரு, தாறுமாறாயிரு, புறப்படு."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to depart, to turn aside"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to depart"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to go wrong, to go crooked"},{"paragraph":"2) devious, perverse (participle)"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be lost from view"},{"paragraph":"2) to become devious"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>turn</i> aside (compare <a href=\"#/H3867 - לָוָה - lâvâh - law-vaw'/3867\">H3867</a>, <a href=\"#/H3874 - לוּט - lûwṭ - loot/3874\">H3874</a> and <a href=\"#/H3885 - לוּן - lûwn - loon/3885\">H3885</a>), that is, (literally) to <i>depart</i>, (figuratively) <i>be perverse: - </i>depart, froward, perverse (-ness)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3868 - לוּז - lûwz - looz/3868\">H3868</a>, <a href=\"#/H3869 - לוּז - lûwz - looz/3869\">H3869</a>, <a href=\"#/H3870 - לוּז - Lûwz - looz/3870\">H3870</a>, <a href=\"#/H3891 - לְזוּת - lᵉzûwth - lez-ooth'/3891\">H3891</a>"}]}